                <LineBreak/>
                You've got the hatred that you<LineBreak/>
                You've always hated in you<LineBreak/>
                You've got to face them now<LineBreak/>
                <LineBreak/>
                Try to stay away<LineBreak/>
                From where the wild things play<LineBreak/>
                (La la la la la)<LineBreak/>
                [x2]<LineBreak/>
                <LineBreak/>
                If you waltz with the wild things<LineBreak/>
